        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> <font color=red>Found this on Casters realm </font id=red><BR>-----------------------------</P><P>A number of new spell effects for Caster Focus items have been added to the spell data file on Test.</P><P>The effects of these are only guessed at by our members on the Casters Realm team but the new effects do show some interesting potential for new caster items.</P><P>Note that these are only on Test Server and may change before going live.</P><P>    * Reagent Conservation - Percent chance to not use a component on spells.<BR>    * Extended Enhancement - Percent increase on duration of buffs.<BR>    * Improved Damage - Percent increase on DD spells.<BR>    * Spell Haste - Percent reduction on casting time of dd's, heal's).<BR>    * Mana Preservation - Percent reduction in mana cost of dd's, heal's).<BR>    * Improved Healing - Percent increase in amount healed.<BR>    * Extended Range - Percent increase in spell range to target.<BR>    * Summoning Haste - Percent reduction in time of summoned objects (non-undead pets only).<BR>    * Summoning Efficiency - Percent reduction in mana cost of summoned items (non-undead pets only).<BR>    * Enhancement Haste - Percent reduction in casting of buff spells.<BR>    * Affliction Efficiency - Percent reduction in mana cost of dots.<BR>    * Extended Affliction - Percent increase in duration of dot's, more ticks, same damage per tick as prior, more total damage.<BR>    * Reanimation Haste - Percent reduction time in casting undead pets (undead pets only).<BR>    * Reanimation Efficiency - Percent reduction in mana cost of undead pets (undead pets only).</P><P></font></td>

      </tr>

